about a little bypass surgery

22:08.300 --> 22:10.500
20 years down the road?
Relax.

22:10.400 --> 22:13.100
You're gonna get the shrimp cocktail
and the poached lobster.

22:15.400 --> 22:17.100
Who's next?

22:18.000 --> 22:20.900
Not bad for a kid
learning the ropes.

22:20.800 --> 22:23.300
Welcome aboard, Greta.

22:23.200 --> 22:24.900
Thanks.

22:24.800 --> 22:27.900
Hey, that seafaring lingo
that you do--

22:27.900 --> 22:30.100
you don't do that
all the time, right?

22:30.100 --> 22:33.200
Yeah, I want to see a collar
from now on.

22:33.200 --> 22:35.500
This is a respectable place.

22:35.500 --> 22:37.700
Aye aye, Captain.

22:37.600 --> 22:39.800
Oh my God.

22:41.300 --> 22:45.300
Hey, you got a car?

22:45.200 --> 22:49.300
Seeing as I don't have a license, no.

22:49.100 --> 22:51.500
Yeah, well,

22:51.400 --> 22:53.500
