23:21.900 --> 23:25.200
Does Lou know that you're
feeding his food to the strays?

23:25.100 --> 23:26.300
It's just garbage.

23:26.200 --> 23:29.600
Lou know that you think
his food is garbage?

23:29.500 --> 23:31.700
No, I mean it's going
in the garbage.

23:31.600 --> 23:33.800
It's just a joke.

23:33.800 --> 23:34.900
Hold on.

23:36.300 --> 23:38.800
My name's Julie.

23:40.500 --> 23:42.500
I'm Greta,

23:42.400 --> 23:46.000
