anagram for "great."

23:45.900 --> 23:48.000
Okay.

23:47.900 --> 23:49.800
You didn't thank me
for getting you hired.

23:49.700 --> 23:52.200
That's 'cause I already
hate the job.

23:54.400 --> 23:57.800
It's only been one day.

