25:12.300 --> 25:14.300
Woman: What are you
looking at?

25:14.200 --> 25:16.500
( men and women arguing )

25:16.400 --> 25:19.100
Man: What did I say?
What did I just say?

25:19.000 --> 25:21.300
Woman: I'm not giving it to you
no matter what.

25:28.500 --> 25:31.000
( siren whooping )

25:47.000 --> 25:49.500
Parnelli.

25:49.400 --> 25:51.800
Where are you?

25:53.300 --> 25:56.000
Parnelli, time to come in.

25:55.800 --> 25:57.800
( police radio chatter )

25:57.800 --> 26:01.100
Parnelli.

26:05.600 --> 26:07.000
Thanks for the ride.

26:07.000 --> 26:09.400
- Stay out of trouble, sweetheart.
- Yeah.

26:09.300 --> 26:11.900
Grams, don't worry.

26:11.800 --> 26:15.300
They're trumped up charges.
Jury's got nothing on me.

26:15.100 --> 26:17.400
What?

26:17.400 --> 26:20.200
We found her over
in Asbury Park.

26:20.100 --> 26:22.200
