from Asbury Park.

26:53.000 --> 26:55.400
Well, you piqued
my curiosity, okay?

26:55.300 --> 26:57.600
Oh, I see.
It was all my fault.

26:57.600 --> 26:59.600
If you don't want me
to do something,

26:59.500 --> 27:02.500
