¶ Yeah, she's mine. ¶

36:00.600 --> 36:02.300
She must have been pretty.

36:02.200 --> 36:03.400
Who?

36:03.400 --> 36:05.900
RS.

36:05.700 --> 36:08.600
RS was a he.

36:09.800 --> 36:12.200
No, not like that.

36:12.200 --> 36:14.100
He was a good friend of mine.

36:14.100 --> 36:16.400
Does he have your initials
tattooed on his wrist?

36:16.400 --> 36:17.900
No.

36:17.800 --> 36:20.100
Why not?

36:20.000 --> 36:22.500
'Cause I'm not dead.

36:25.100 --> 36:27.600
( distant train horn whistles )

36:29.000 --> 36:31.200
Is this what you guys do
for fun around here?

36:31.100 --> 36:33.400
I kind of try
not to have fun.

36:33.300 --> 36:36.300
I try to stay working.

36:36.200 --> 36:38.500
I got this great talent
for finding trouble

36:38.500 --> 36:40.900
and getting all up in it,

36:40.800 --> 36:42.800
so I stay busy.

36:43.700 --> 36:46.400
You want to be a chef?

36:46.400 --> 36:49.600
Yeah, I want my own restaurant.

36:49.500 --> 36:51.800
Where did you learn
how to cook anyway,

36:51.700 --> 36:54.200
home ec?

36:55.600 --> 36:58.100
No, prison.

36:58.100 --> 37:00.700
You lie.

37:02.000 --> 37:04.400
No, for real.
I was at juvie.

37:04.300 --> 37:06.000
I was younger then.

37:06.000 --> 37:07.600
What were you in for?

37:07.600 --> 37:10.200
Joyriding.

37:11.400 --> 37:13.800
( harrumphs )
You're full of it.

37:13.800 --> 37:17.000
I mean, it's not something
I'm trying to brag about.

37:16.900 --> 37:19.700
I'm not proud of it.

37:22.100 --> 37:25.500
Stealing cars, huh?

37:25.400 --> 37:27.800
That's joyriding.

37:27.700 --> 37:29.800
But I'm not into that anymore.

37:29.800 --> 37:33.100
So the correctional system

37:33.000 --> 37:34.700
totally corrected you.

37:34.700 --> 37:38.700
Let me tell you something--

37:38.500 --> 37:41.200
it's a miracle
that I'm even on the outside.

37:41.100 --> 37:45.400
Where I'm at--
I did that, you know.

37:45.200 --> 37:48.700
So if I go back--
I did that too.

37:52.500 --> 37:54.000
That's cool.

37:53.900 --> 37:56.100
Yeah.

37:56.000 --> 37:59.500
But you'd still steal me
a BMW, right?

37:59.400 --> 38:01.800
For you-- anything.
I got you.

38:01.700 --> 38:03.800
I just don't know
why you don't like my BMX.

38:03.700 --> 38:06.800
It's the sickest right here.

38:09.600 --> 38:12.100
